data.description: Welcome to your dream Florida pool home! This charming home is nestled in the heart of Port St Lucie. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by a bright and spacious living area overlooking your resort style backyard that features a custom sparkling salt water pool, screened enclosure, and lush tropical landscaping. Some of the many other features include: Crown molding, paver driveway and patio, stone accents on exterior, pool heater with chiller, newer pool equipment, fully fenced yard, stainless appliances, 3 stage reverse osmosis system, plus much more. Furniture is negotiable. Purchase this home fully furnished and you have an amazing home already set up for an Airbnb. Sellers will also entertain a 6 month lease purchase option. Schedule your private viewing today
